net.datacrow.core.console

Interface IMasterView


  • public interface IMasterView
    Interface for the MasterView. The master view manages the various view types for a single DcModule. The module dictates the available views, which are then registered here. The MasterView manages the updates, removals and addition of items to the views it manages.
    Author:
    Robert Jan van der Waals
